{"tid":229254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為趕赴現場涉駕警車超速兼衝紅燈 交通警被控危險駕駛","createTime":"2017-05-04T12:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T15:10:12.000Z","uid":28366,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc20967936dc24a2eef29f568d4f7a09ff1e1779","tid":229254,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170504/large/1493894623_ddfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170504%2Flarge%2F1493894623_ddfc.jpg&h=9fbfff73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">當日警車撞壆，車頭嚴重損毁</span><br />\n<br />\n交通警員去年駕駛警車執勤期間，為趕往一宗輕微交通意外的現場，疑衝紅燈並於限速每小時100公里的粉嶺公路上超速，以每小時136公里行駛，最終這部車價13萬元的警車失控撞壆，日後若維修則要花15萬元。交通警被控危險駕駛罪。案件經審訊後今被裁定表證成立，裁判官將押至5月19日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n被告為新界北交通意外調查隊高級警員魏熾強，他於去年7月5日清晨5時，接報需往吐露港近中文大學調查一宗的士及小巴相撞的交通意外。控方指當日正值天雨，被告駕駛一輛設有道路監察攝影機的警車，於粉嶺公路一個彎位失控撞壆，事後警車車頭嚴重損毀，更發現被告於行車期間衝紅燈，整個過程被車內攝影機拍攝下來。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170504/56651054\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170504%2F56651054&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=8e4f06de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170504%2F56651054&h=a338dbc8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170504/56651054</a>"},{"pid":"4031d87ee640f5efda9e5c3c4e498bfe935591e4","tid":229254,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e39d6122bb4f9780f5acc176eabdead87d1abd","tid":229254,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CAK